data.description: Explore the possibilities of this charming home featuring 3 spacious bedrooms, two living room areas, and a versatile flex space with water access. Updated fixtures, skylights, and a generous backyard add to its allure. This property encourages your creative touch, whether it’s expanding the laundry, crafting an entertaining area, or setting up a home office. With a touch of TLC, seize the chance to shape a space that aligns with your lifestyle. The large kitchen, living, and dining areas offer ample room for entertaining, family gatherings, and intimate get-togethers, facilitated by an open layout for seamless adaptability. Investor opportunity, sold as-is. See attached documents.
